---
title: Quick Tex-Mex Double Baked Chicken & Zesty Veggie Fries with Slaw & Smokey Aioli
description: A touch of zest never fails to make a chicken dinner glow up into a stellar standout. The veggie fries are zested and the baked chicken is seasoned in our fan-favourite Tex-Mex blend. What adds the final touch though is the smokey aioli. It’s a picture (and deliciously) perfect dinner!
